  "instructions_to_main_agent": [
    "1. THEME: Implement the 'dark' class by default on the HTML tag. Create a toggle that swaps the class.",
    "2. NAVBAR: Make it sticky with 'backdrop-blur-xl' and a subtle bottom border. It should float 20px from top on scroll if possible, or stick to top.",
    "3. HERO: Split layout. Left: Typography + CTAs. Right: The 'hero_background' image masked inside a 3D-tilted card or a video player mock.",
    "4. BENTO GRID: For the 'Features' section, use the 'tracing beam' effect (animated border) on hover for the cards.",
    "5. TESTIMONIALS: Use a horizontal marquee (infinite scroll). Do NOT use a static grid.",
    "6. FOOTER: Massive typography. The brand name 'RIXLY' should span the entire container width at the bottom.",
    "7. MICRO-INTERACTIONS: All buttons must scale down (scale-95) on click. All links must have a hover color change.",
    "8. ACCESSIBILITY: Ensure text contrast. The primary color is bright (#FF6B4A), so use black text on top of it, or white if bold/large enough.",
    "9. DO NOT use gradients for backgrounds. Use solid colors with subtle noise or the provided image urls as low-opacity overlays."
  ],
  "UNIVERSAL_GUIDELINES_FOR_MAIN_AGENT": [
    "- Don't make generic centered layouts.",
    "- Use 2-3x more spacing than feels comfortable (py-24, py-32).",
    "- Never use pure black (#000000). Use #02040A.",
    "- Use 'Outfit' font for all Headings (font-bold or font-extrabold).",
    "- Use 'DM Sans' for all Body text.",
    "- Add 'data-testid' to all interactive elements."
  ]
